Orlando Pirates coach Milutin "Micho" Sredojevic resigned because he is facing charges of indecent exposure after he allegedly tried to force himself on a hotel cleaner. Sunday World can reveal a case was opened against Sredojevic at the Norwood police station in Joburg following the incident at the Protea Hotel Wanderers in Illovo, Joburg. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD 